======== BUGS ========
i had run into problems, especially th option problem and the start of this project and at the end,

the problem: the options for the next and prv question is not existing, untill next or prv question is called, 
this made it hard for me to style the options 
why?
when you click on an option it is styled, and immiediately you go to the nextit loses it styling because 
it no longer exist in the dorm, now when you come back to it there is no applied style becausefunctions only run once in js, i fixed this by making each option an object and when a style is clicked i save its own global obj 
since global obj doesnt change and based



2.A friend of mine found a bug - in summary 👇👇👇
  when you click next question button to go to the next page , continuous hitting the keyboard
   "enterkey" will cause the next function to keep on runing, this does not break it, but what it breaks is when the enter key is held 
  
  what code logic when enterkey is held:
   the question skips with speed to the next question, eventually it reaching the last quetion,
   when it reaches end the same next question function has an `if` statement inside it, which calls functions that calculates and display the score once you click the nextfunction again i.e after reaching the last question, it calculates the score perfectly .
   but because the enter key is held down it recalulates your score adding or subtracting it again and again which is bad. 

   note: the bug only happen when the nextbtn is in focus and you hold down the enterkey which iterate the questions with speed,
         it does not happen by consecutively clicking on the enterkey
   note: only  destop users has the possiblity to experience this !!

   fix: I fixed number (2) by making submit its own function and adding submit btn at the page,
        then called the functions that calcalute and display result inside it. so when you click 
        next btn which calls the nextquestionfunction ... holding enterkey will skip questions fast 
        and take you to the last question this time  nothing will happen because i removed the functions
        needed for calcaluting and displaying result and included it in the submit btn function.

         the submit btn is available from the start of the question till the last quesstion, this is a new feature
         because some users whould want to submit earlier than required even tho not finished all questions, as in real life

         



